exceptions: IllegalArgumentException - if this enum class has no constant with the specified name
methods.description: Returns the enum constant of this class with the specified name. The string must match exactly an identifier used to declare an enum constant in this class. (Extraneous whitespace characters are not permitted.)

enum_constants.name: UNIVERSAL
enum_constants.description: Universal key bindings are used in every context and will conflict with any other context. Key Bindings are universal by default.

enum_constants.name: GUI
enum_constants.description: Gui key bindings are only used when a Screen is open.

enum_constants.name: IN_GAME
enum_constants.description: In-game key bindings are only used when a Screen is not open.
